      "body": [
        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "label": "Recto",
          "value": "<ol>\n<li>\n<p>In the name of God the Merciful and Compassionate.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>I inform the exalted and glorious presence, the Iksh\u012bl and Master of the Horses\u2014may God prolong his life and cause</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>his well-being, success, protection and safety to endure, and cause his power to endure in happiness\u2014that my son-in-law, who is called Ab\u016b \u02bfAbd All\u0101h Mu\u1e25ammad</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>ibn \u02bfAbd al-Ra\u1e25m\u0101n, the merchant, has set off (to you). He has suffered the loss of a debt owed to him by some spendthrift people known as the sons of Kajja, namely Mak\u0101rim, Mu\u1e25ibb and Faraj.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>This Mak\u0101rim stood guarantor for his brother Mu\u1e25ibb with regard to his part of the debt that was owed to him (my son-in-law) by them with the testimony of a group of travellers</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>to the land of Mar\u012bs and undertook to pay his debt for him and reclaim from him what he owes, his debts and his possessions. This is the greatest of my requests</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>to you. May God, the Exalted, grant me in you the fairest arbiter. I have sent him to you, please pay his debt and help him stand on his own feet in the best possible way.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>You know the importance of a son-in-law for his father-in-law. If he could have a little help in his predicament, quickly without</p>\n</li>\n</ol>",
          "format": "text/html"
        }
      ],
      "motivation": [
        "sc:supplementing",
        "translating"
      ],
      "schema:position": 1
    },
